GG_BKH_HARBOR
This is a map that I created for gungame, but here are buy-zones included. The map has 40 spawnpoints with a custom 3D skybox, 3 tunnels, two bridges, one is a rope bridge, the other an arched bridge. Plenty of displacements, docks and water. Please leave any feedback that can help improve the map. Thanks to Karatekaefer for the customskybox. Thanks to Trappa Keepa for the custom sound.
